      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this fantastic find! This vehicle is in truly good condition, having been well-maintained and cared for over the years. It runs smoothly and looks great, making it a reliable and stylish choice for its next owner. While it shows some light, honest signs of use, it\u2019s a solid, road-ready car that\u2019s ready for many more adventures!",
